Name: Agent Focus: Ellen
Desc: Use it to obtain the Agent or unlock the Agent's Mindscapes.
Desc2:
Snapshots from Ellen's daily life and from in combat, recording important moments before and after she became an Agent.
These images also provide insights into her fighting style and favorite weapons, helping to better understand her strengths.

Ellen looks serious and a little stiff. Some of her poses... look as though other girls from her school had a hand in coaching her.
